## 四、技术实现建议

### 4.1 核心数据表

```sql
-- 用户表
users (id, phone, nickname, avatar, created_at)

-- 余额账户表
wallets (user_id, balance, total_earned, total_spent, total_withdrawn)

-- 余额流水表
wallet_transactions (id, user_id, type, amount, description, created_at)

-- 商品表
products (id, name, brand, category, original_price, resale_rate, stock)

-- 订单表
orders (id, user_id, total_amount, balance_used, cash_paid, status, created_at)

-- 回收订单表
recycles (id, user_id, product_id, order_id, condition, estimated_price, final_price, status)

-- 会员表
memberships (user_id, level, started_at, expired_at)
```

### 4.2 关键接口

- `GET /api/products/:id` - 商品详情（含回收价）
- `POST /api/recycle/estimate` - 预估回收价
- `POST /api/recycle/apply` - 申请回收
- `GET /api/wallet` - 查询余额
- `POST /api/wallet/withdraw` - 余额提现
- `POST /api/orders` - 创建订单（支持余额支付）

